DNV-OS-C401 FABRICATION AND TESTING OF OFFSHORE STRUCTURES JANUARY 2001 DET NORSKE VERITAS is an autonomous and independent foundation with the objectives of safeguarding life, property and the environment. DNV undertakes classification, certification, verification and consultancy services relating to quality of ships, offshore units and installations.
